tang - 采桑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Hy-Di/author-sG1m4LG8HNG0zx1xauXNmA">Lưu Hy Di</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-I/poem-WUn1VdvYiysfzxuNguNWhQ">Thuỷ điệu ca (I) - 水調歌（I）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-Nh%E1%BB%A5/V%C4%83n-quy%C3%AAn/poem-F3foq6z0PFnZuSul6ztCZg">Văn quyên - 聞鵑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-Nh%E1%BB%A5/author-_3trYeu7UK2Z6kJllb-KaA">Phương Hiếu Nhụ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-V/poem-9Lj_Z8A-VdwVeRG-X0epNQ">Vô đề (V) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
